Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:03.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:05.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ突然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobato liked yesterday's birthday\Nparty, and it also made me... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:08.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日の誕生パーティー　小鳩も喜んでたし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:13.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も　何つうか　すげえ嬉しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Qu-Quit saying that embarrassing stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:17.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何恥ずかしいこと言ってんのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call it embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:19.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,恥ずかしいとか言うなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. Well, um... This "birthday party"\Nthing turned out to be pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:22.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　そのう　何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誕生日パーティーというものはなかなかいいものだった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all do our best to make\Nfriends we can celebrate birthdays with!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:30.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私達も誕生日を祝えるような友達を作れるよう　頑張ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! This made me realize all over\Nagain how cool it is to have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:35.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今回改めて友達がいるっていいなっとわかったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:36.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マジで頑張ろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's seriously do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's been my plan all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:40.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,言われなくても最初からそのつもりよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wish, Aniki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:41.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,御意です　兄貴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you, Rika?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:45.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ　理科
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then, let's keep\Nworking on the school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:51.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃ　今日からまた学園祭に向けて頑張りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Kodaka-{\i1}sempai?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ　小鷹先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:56.20,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:01.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この時の俺にはまだ　覚悟がなかったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point I wasn't\Nprepared to face things yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though deep down,\NI knew what Rika was trying to say...
