Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a café where you can play\Nwith cats as you drink your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:08.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,猫と触れ合いながらお茶することができる喫茶店ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can such a paradise\Nexist in this rotten world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:12.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この腐った世界にそんなパラダイスが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to do an exhibit for the club {\i1}too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしこっちでも展示なんてやりたくないんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, you said you\Nwere doing one for your class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:18.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういや　クラスでやるって言ってたな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"The History of Toya City," ri...
