Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:20.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggested "The All-Knowing, Almighty\NGoddess Kashiwazaki Sena Feature,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:25.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしは「全知全能の女神柏崎星奈様特集」を提案したのに
