Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:51.70,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前ら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kobato, should you be\Nskipping the middle school's festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういや　小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　中等部のほうの学園祭はいいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your class doing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,クラスで何かやらないの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your class presenting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のクラスの出し物は何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:08.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ククク　我が眷属よ　貴様の知るよしもないことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My kindred, you shall never find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't tell me, I won't\Nmake you any pig-bone ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,言わないと豚骨ラーメン作ってやらないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:17.40,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ククク　高貴なる闇の王レイシス·ヴィ·フェリシティ·煌を脅そうというのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You would try to threaten Raysis Vi\NFelicity Sumeragi, great ruler of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,愚かな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll eat {\i1}all{\i} of yesterday's leftover beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日の肉の残りも全部俺が食う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:23.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ずるい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら素直に言え
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:28.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,映画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,映画ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:31.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,面白そう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A movie, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:33.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,映画か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And? What will {\i1}you{\i} be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:36.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それで　お前は何をやるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ククク　貴様には関わりな…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That is no concern of yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't tell, you're cut off from gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,教えないなら　ゲーム禁止だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...role...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,…役
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:45.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...ng role!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:47.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,し…役
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grole"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:49.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,役
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}leading role,{\i} I said!\NI gotta do the leadin' part now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　主役
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:54.39,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,主役やらんといかへんくなってまったんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The leading role?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,主役
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Kobato!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえじゃ　小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- I want to see it! I {\i1}so{\i} want to see that movie!\N- Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,みたい　その映画超みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:02.15,夏雪日文旁白-ja,,0,0,0,,わかった　わかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kobato, if you're the lead,\Nshould you really be {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,っていうか　小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,主役がこんな所にいていいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you skipped out on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほっぽりだして来たのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobato. It's an honor to\Nbe chosen, so do a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:15.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩　せっかく選ばれたんだからしっかりやれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people who never get\Npicked to do anything in class, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:17.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,世の中には
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:21.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,クラスの中で何の役目ももらえないやつだっているんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何の役目も
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You got the chance,\Nso give it a try, Kobato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかくの機会なんだから頑張ってみろうよ　小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a really great thing to\Nhave people who need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,必要としてくれる人がいるっていうのも本当に凄いことなんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:42.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よーし　それでこそ高貴なる闇の王レイシス·ヴィ·フェリシティ·煌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's my Raysis Vi Felicity\NSumeragi, great ruler of the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall be going, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ　行って来るのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:50.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.43,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,108)}School Festival Ideas
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:57.07,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\pos(398,234)}Movie
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we should make a movie, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:57.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　私達も映画を撮ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika saw this coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そう来ると思っていました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私も異存はありません
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was bound to happen this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　当然の流れよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も賛成だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　決まりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:07.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:08.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika is fine with the decision,\Nbut what will we make it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:12.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,決定はいいんですけど　内容はどうするんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the screenplay to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,脚本は私に任せろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! If we leave it to {\i1}her,{\i}\Nit's 100% obvious that it'll be horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対駄目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:16.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空なんかに任せたら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:19.09,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,百パーセントひどいものになるに決まってるもの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that, Meat? You don't\Nbelieve in my magnificent taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:20.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だと　肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私の素晴らしいセンスが信じられないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:24.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering your record\Nwith the round-robin story...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:27.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空にはリレー小説の時の前科があるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, rest easy.\NI'll take a lesson from my past,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかくこれまでの反省を生かし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and incorporate you\Npeople's opinions as I write.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:35.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様らの意見も取り入れつつ書くから安心するがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's get right down to it: any suggestions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ということで早速だが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か提案はあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No sexual assault, for starters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:40.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とりあえず陵辱は禁止な
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:43.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:44.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　何じゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not{\i} the right reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So she was really planning on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱりやる気だったね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ba-dum! I'm gracing you\Nwith my presence, poopy-heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:51.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,久しぶりに部室に来てやったぞ　うんこども
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Maria-{\i1}sensei{\i} is here too,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マリア先生も来たことですし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,shall we start by pulling\Ntogether everyone's opinions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは皆さんの意見をまとめましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:07:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, does anybody have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　何かアイディアがある者はいるか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a story about a\Ntransfer student who joins the class
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:03.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ある日　クラスにやってきた転校生が
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and is misunderstood and ostracized at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:05.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最初は誤解されて仲間はずれになるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but eventually becomes really popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:08.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やがてクラスの人気者になるってのはどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't play any role that's not a juicy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:11.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしが演じるのは美味しい役でなきゃ駄目よ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat lots of juicy steak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:14.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,美味しいご馳走たくさん食べたいのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to play a samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わたくしはサムライの役がいいです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika thinks a slightly daring love\Nscene between two men is a must!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:21.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,男同士のちょっぴり大胆なラブシーンは外せないと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it even possible to pull all that together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.95,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(700,200)\bord4\be4}Transfer student gets popular\NJuicy Meat\NJuicy steak\NSamurai appears\NBoy-on-boy action
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:24.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これでちゃんとまとめられるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch: I'll make it the\Nmasterpiece of the century.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:28.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私の力で世紀の大傑作にしてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しみにしているがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:36.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ　こんな時間に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.64,Default - Style 01,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\be4\fs40\an7\pos(490,220)\frz4.98}\h\h\h\h{\c&HE8DCCD&\3c&H574230&}Mikazuki Yozora\N\h\h\h\hTomorrow\N\N\N\N{\c&H574230&\3c&HE8DCCD&\fs48}Body: I'm going to\Nsee a movie to get\Nsome ideas. You\Ncan come along if\Nyou're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:41.16,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\be3\an7\pos(90,40)}I don't *need* to go with anyone or whatever since all you do at a movie\Nis shut up and watch, but I figure if you have one you want to see, I'm\Nwilling to go with you while I'm at it, that's all. If you're not interested\Nin movies, whatever, I'll just go by myself, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Her messages are always so rambling...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:43.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相変わらず回りくどいメールだな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess it does make sense to\Nstudy a real movie before we start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,けど　確かに本物の映画を見て勉強するってのはありか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, tomorrow the club can...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃ明日は皆で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:54.32,Default - Style 01,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\an7\pos(180,124)\frz26.47\fscx80}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hMikazuki Yozora\N\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hNo subject\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fscx100}oh don't tell the others cuz\N\Nthere's no point in bringing a crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You typed that in a hurry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よっぽと急いで打ったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't tell the others," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかへの連絡不要か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.72,Default - Style 01,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\an7\fs40\pos(470,272)\frz4.197}\h\h\h\h\hMikazuki Yozora\N\h\h\h\h\hRe: No subject\N\N\N\NUnderstate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, don't tell me you\Nseriously mean to keep up that look?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　まさか　マジでその格好で通すつもりなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:17.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:27.61,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Cinémathèque Toya"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are we watching today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,で　今日は何を見るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really picked one out.\NWe'll just pick from whatever's playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,特に決めてない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:34.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,上映しているものの中から適当に選ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that pretty slapdash?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなでいいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how I always watch movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私はいつもこんな感じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これにするか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems kinda unexciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か地味だな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No good for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:48.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いやなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, n-no, this one's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ああいや　いいよ　これで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C'est si bon!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,セシボーン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C'est si bon?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C'est si bon.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C'est si bon!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:09:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- C'est si bon, c'est si bon.{\i}\N{\i1}- C'est si bon, c'est si bon...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... was that useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.20,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのう　参考になったか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! Idiot! I didn't\Nthink it would be so disgraceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:09.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なるか　馬鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか　あんな破廉恥な内容だとは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だよな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,B-By the way, Kodaka... do you...\Nwant to do {\i1}c-c'est si bon{\i} stuff too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:21.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,と　ところで小鷹もセシボーンのことをしたいと思うのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:23.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,N-N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's have some tea\Nwhile we're out and about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:28.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　せっかくだからお茶でも飲んで行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a café right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:31.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,喫茶店ならそこに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's another one\NI really need to try. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:35.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　どうしても確認しておきたい店がある　行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:37.85,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\be3\pos(692,266)\}Covered in Kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:37.85,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\be3\an7\pos(704,394)}It's\NOK to pet us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:45.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,にゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Meow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:48.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,にゃんって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:52.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, you caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:57.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,捕まった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You really love cats, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:02.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　よっぽと猫が好きなんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as\Na person who hates cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,猫が嫌いな人間などいない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have one at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:07.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,家では飼ってないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we live in an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うちはアパートだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:11.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえばそうだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if I weren't in an\Napartment, I doubt I'd ever get a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとも　アパートでなかったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:17.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私が猫を飼うことはないだろうがな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:18.40,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何でだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember Night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ナイトのことを覚えているか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mere, Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おいで　ナイト
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:48.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ナイト
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:11:00.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ナイト…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad when someone suddenly disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.79,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いきなりいなくなってしまうのは悲しいものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,悲しい思いをするくらいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want us to really\Nbond if they'll just make me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,深い絆なんていらない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,適度にじゃれ合ってるだけでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with just playing\Ntogether and not taking it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Kodaka. Look forward to my script.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:21.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあな　小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,脚本楽しみにしているがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何と言うか　今日はそのう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, today sort of made me feel like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:30.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"That"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:31.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Like things were ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,10年前みたいだった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. It did feel like\Nthose days for me, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:37.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:41.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにちょっとだけあの頃みたいな気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you, Kodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:45.68,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃあな　小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:55.06,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\pos(368,372)\c&H42EED9&}King
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:55.06,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\pos(682,372)}Horse
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:58.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,脚本が完成したぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The screenplay is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I'm very pleased\Nwith it. Accept it with respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,正直会心のできだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心して受け取るがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can start filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:05.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これで撮影に取りかかりますね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,で　何のつもり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:13.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ククク　わ　我が名はレイシス·ヴィ·何とか的な…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My name is Raysis Vi Something Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}faker!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この紛い物が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やるじゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is way extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:22.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マジぱないです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Yozora-{\i1}sempai{\i} really write this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これ本当に夜空先輩が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is seriously good stuff. Are you a genius?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マジでいいよ　これ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　天才か
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.90,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:31.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's decided: this will\Nbe our script. Next is casting...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　脚本はこれで決定ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,では配役ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The cast is already set.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,キャストならすでに決まっている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, I'll be the lead, Kuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まず主人公の空也は私だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The transfer student, Kuya's former\Nbest friend Hirotaka, is Kodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:45.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,空也のかつての親友で転校生の広孝に小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sana, the class star who\Nopposes them to the end, is Meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:50.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この二人に最後まで敵対するクラスの中心人物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:51.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,紗菜が肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobuyuki, the timid boy who secretly\Nadmires the manly Hirotaka, is Yukimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:57.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,男らしい広孝にひそかに憧れている内気な少年伸行が幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:58.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika, who always plays malicious\Ntricks on Kuya for being with Hirotaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:00.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,広孝と一緒にいる空也に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:02.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,悪質な嫌がらせを繰り返す芹香が理科
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, the little sister Kuya\Ndoesn't get along with, is Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:07.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,空也と中が悪い妹の麻梨がマリアだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:11.83,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(700,100)\bord4\be4}Cast:\N\h\h\hKuya... Me\N\h\h\hHirotaka... Kodaka\N\h\h\hSana... Meat\N\h\h\hNobuyuki... Yukimura\N\h\h\hSerika... Rika\N\h\h\hMari... Maria
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だかよくわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Isn't it perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ　ぴったりだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:13.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,異議あり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Meat? Is there some sort of problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ肉　何か問題でも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you're the\Nleading role and I'm the villain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:18.70,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何であんたが主役で　あたしが悪役なのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the script objectively\Nand made the logical choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:22.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,客観的に脚本を読み　冷静に判断した結果だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In particular, Sana is gorgeous\Nin appearance and the class star.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:26.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,特に紗菜は華やかな見てくれのクラスの中心人物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it pains me to admit it, she\Nobviously has a lot in common with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.39,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しゃくだが貴様と重なる部分も多いだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Various circumstances have made her warped,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:31.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いろいろあって屈折してはいるが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's good at heart\Nand has lots of good scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,根はいいやつだし　見せ場も多い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's quite a {\i1}juicy{\i} role.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,かなり「美味しい」役だと思うが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, that might be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:40.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そう言われてみれば　そうかも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll use this cast for...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,では配役はこれで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:44.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Rika? More objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ　理科　まだあるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika has no problem with casting\Nbased on appearances and personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:50.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,外形や雰囲気で役を決めるのは問題ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we use that logic,\NI think Kodaka-{\i1}sempai{\i} is miscast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:51.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その理屈で言えば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹先輩の役は違うと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:55.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の役
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakagawa Hirotaka is a 17-year-old boy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,中川広孝　17才　男
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,with a strong sense of justice and\Nan honest and stouthearted nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:03.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,正義感が強く　実直且つ剛毅な性格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a popular, sociable guy\Nwith a strong sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,社交的でユーモアのセンスもある人気者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's smart {\i1}and{\i} athletic,\Nand tall, and has manly features.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:10.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勉強も運動も出来　背が高くて顔も凛々しい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, I'm a perfect fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にぴったりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that Kodaka-{\i1}sempai{\i}\Ndoesn't fit the part!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:15.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなのどう考えても小鷹先輩に合ってないじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, she noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:17.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気付かれたか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, "noticed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:20.03,夏雪日文旁白-ja,,0,0,0,,気付かれたかって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,True, Hirotaka and Kodaka are\Nabout as different as you can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:23.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに小鷹と広孝では　イメージがあってないにも程があるわね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Big Brother isn't\Ncool at all on the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんは見た目は全然格好良くないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yozora-{\i1}sempai,{\i} why is Kodaka-{\i1}sempai{\i} Hirotaka?\N- At all... At {\i1}all?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空先輩　どうして小鷹先輩が広孝なんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:29.54,夏雪日文旁白-ja,,0,0,0,,全然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:31.51,夏雪日文旁白-ja,,0,0,0,,全然か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodaka was my childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹は私の幼なじみだから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, he was, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.40,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえばそうだったわね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Hirotaka and Kuya were childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:44.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　広孝と空也は幼なじみだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore I chose my real-life\Nchildhood friend Kodaka to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:48.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だから私とリアル幼なじみの小鷹を広孝役に選んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's weird about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.79,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それの何がおかしい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not {\i1}weird,{\i} but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:52.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,べ　別におかしいとかじゃないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That means that if you aren't Kuya,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:55.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ということは　夜空先輩が空也でなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there ceases to be any reason for\NKodaka-{\i1}sempai{\i} to be Hirotaka, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:59.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,広孝が小鷹先輩である理由もなくなるわけですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　それは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we decide on the casting by vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:04.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは一つ　配役を投票で決めるというのどうです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:06.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それがいいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't decide that on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勝手に決めるな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear, so you're not\Nconfident you'll be chosen as Kuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おや　空也に選ばれる自信がないんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. The results are obvious anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:13.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ結果など見えている
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:15.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ballot Box"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.36,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\be4\an7\pos(750,110)}Hirotaka... Yozora-{\i1}sempai{\i}\N Sana... Maria-{\i1}san{\i}\NNobuyuki... Rika\NMari... Kodaka-{\i1}sempai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the results of the vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:20.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,投票の結果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:23.03,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\be4\an7\pos(750,110)}Kuya... Yukimura-{\i1}kun{\i}\NHirotaka... Yozora-{\i1}sempai{\i}\NSana... Maria-{\i1}san{\i}\NSerika... Sena-{\i1}sempai{\i}\NNobuyuki... Rika\NMari... Kodaka-{\i1}sempai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,配役はこうなりました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:27.17,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad2\an8\pos(1102,380)\3c&H343839&\4c&H47585F&\b1}Kuya\N\h\h\h\h\h(lead)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:27.17,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad4\c&HCCD6FB&\3c&H3946E2&\4c&H344268&\pos(166,436)\b1}Kusunoki\NYukimura
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... the leading role?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:27.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わたくしが主役ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.17,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad4\an8\c&HF095E6&\3c&H781F71&\4c&H3F263C&\pos(1129,312)\b1}Mikazuki\NYozora
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.17,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad2\an7\pos(180,440)\4c&H626767&\b1}Hirotaka\N\h\h\h\h(best friend)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ 何たることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! I'm a cool boss lady now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.94,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad2\an7\pos(1020,300)\4c&H626767&\b1}Sana\N\h\h\h{\fscx90}(class boss)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.94,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\shad3\bord4\c&HFFF5D0&\3c&HA74945&\4c&H632B2C&\pos(140,360)\b1}Takayama\NMaria
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! I'm a cool boss lady now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私が偉いポスの女になったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.81,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad4\pos(880,518)\c&H95F5F7&\3c&H279EEE&\4c&H3E4D78&\b1}Kashiwazaki Sena
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.81,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\shad3\bord4\an7\pos(226,342)\4c&H626767&\b1}Serika\N\h\h\h(likes Hirotaka)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:36.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,な　何で
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:40.52,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\shad3\bord4\an7\pos(1000,360)\4c&H5A5A5A&\b1}Nobuyuki\N\h\h\h{\fscx70}(admires Hirotaka)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:40.52,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\shad4\bord4\pos(380,400)\b1\c&HCCFFEF&\3c&H14B459&\4c&H2A6152&}Shiguma\NRika
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika's playing the younger boy, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:39.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理科が少年役ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何でこうなる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:45.19,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\shad3\bord4\pos(930,380)\c&H91D1E8&\3c&H093C4D&\4c&H3D6573&\b1}Hasegawa\NKodaka
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:45.19,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad2\an7\pos(233,329)\4c&H626767&\3c&H363636&\b1}Mari\N(Kuya's little {\3c&H6313DE&}sister{\3c&H363636&})
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:45.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誰だよ　俺を妹役に押したやつは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who picked me for the little-sister part?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:50.83,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前か
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I thought it might be a\Nlittle fun, so I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:54.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと面白そうかなって思ったんだから　しょうがないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that gave you no choice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこにしょうがない要素がある
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:16:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, it wasn't just me! You got two votes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それにあたしだけじゃないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:15:59.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,2票入ってたんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一人は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:02.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何でマリアが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Big Brother is always a big brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:06.60,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんはな　いつもお兄ちゃんなので
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought it might be a nice change\Nto do a non-big-brother Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:10.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,たまにはお兄ちゃんじゃなくなったお兄ちゃんというのもいいなと思ったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, our various ulterior motives\Nturned this into very strange casting...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,皆さんの思わくが絡まりあった結果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:18.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よくわからない配役になってしまいましたね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't actually do that, can we?\NWhy don't we vote one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:20.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でもそれはさすがになしだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度投票し直すってと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.19,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(1072,369)\bord4\shad2\3c&H363635&\4c&H56686F&\b1}Kuya\N\h\h\h( {\c&HB0FFFF&\3c&H29AFF6&\4c&H71D8F1&}lead{\3c&H363635&\4c&H56686F&\c&HFFFFFF&} )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.19,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad4\c&HCCD6FB&\3c&H3946E2&\4c&H344268&\pos(130,360)\b1}Kusunoki\NYukimura
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Yukimura... Do your best in the lead, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのう　幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,主役　頑張れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I shall work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　頑張らせていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,で　俺の役どうしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what do I do about my part?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll change Mari to a little brother.\NIt won't harm the story any.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.15,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,麻梨は弟に変更する
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.40,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ストリー上不都合はないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Got a complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:46.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ　文句でもあるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I... I'm just a little sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:49.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　そのう　ちょっと　御免
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I ended up making more work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:54.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,余計な手間を掛けさせることになっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being creepy. Did you get\Ninfected by some kind of evil bacteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:58.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気持ち悪いな　悪質な病原菌にでも感染したのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:16:59.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うるさいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This script was pretty good, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:03.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この脚本が割りとよかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! It's no trouble to change\Na sister to a brother or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:09.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,別に妹を弟にするくらい大した手間ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really? Well, that's all right then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:10.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　そう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら　いいんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,で　何だよ　これ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell is this?\NIt's a totally different story now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,全然違う話になってるじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:28.83,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気のせいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No he's not! Who the heck is this "Kotaro" guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気のせいじゃないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:33.16,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\an8\pos(464,53)}Kotaro
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何よ　この小太郎ってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuya's little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,空也の弟だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know {\i1}that.{\i} What I'm asking is,\Nwhy are they suddenly twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことはわかってるわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:38.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いてるのはなんで空也が双子になってるかってのことよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari wasn't her twin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:40.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,麻梨の時は違ったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And the role is substantially more\Nimportant, too, with more screen time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:44.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その上出番も重要性も大幅に増してますね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus Kuya and Hirotaka are talking\Nkind of coldly to each other now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:48.54,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に広孝と空也のやり取りが何だか余所余所しくなってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. The truth is, Kuya and\NHirotaka weren't particularly close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:52.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,実は広孝と空也は別に仲良くなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But they're best friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,親友だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. To Hirotaka, Kuya\Nwas like a friend of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:55.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　違う
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:59.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,広孝にとって空也は　友達の友達的な関係だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She was always with Kotaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:01.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小太郎と何時も一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so the three of them all\Nended up hanging out, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とりあえず三人組みで過ごしていただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel bad for poor Kuya?\NWhy not let all three be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:06.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,空也が可哀想過ぎだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,仲良し三人組でいいじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodaka. A "friend of a\Nfriend" is {\i1}not{\i} a "friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:12.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹　友達の友達はな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,友達じゃないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Their relationship isn't a\Nteam of three. It's two plus one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:17.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつらの関係は三人組ではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二人プラス一人なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that sounds familiar, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それは身に覚えあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second! Why make\NKuya the odd one out, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:26.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だとしても　何で空也のほう一人にするのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make it Kotaro instead,\Nyou don't have to change the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:27.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小太郎一人サイドにすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ストリーを変えなくても済むじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それは出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:32.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何でよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's more natural for\Nhim to get along with Kotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小太郎と仲がいいほうは自然だからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Kodaka is playing Kotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:37.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹が小太郎役だし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Kodaka was your\Nchildhood friend, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:43.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それって小鷹があんたの幼なじみだからってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was forever ago. It doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:49.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな昔のこと　今はどうでもいいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:54.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だと　肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What{\i} did you say, Meat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,き　貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"D-Doesn't matter," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:05.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ど　どうでもいいだと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It doesn't matter whether\Nyou and Kodaka used to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:09.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　あんたと小鷹が友達だったとか　どうでもいいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What you need to do right now is\Nrevise this script right, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたが今やらなきゃいけないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,脚本をちゃんと修正することでしょうが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you! You don't know how I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:18.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様　私がどんな気持ちで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you it doesn't {\i1}matter{\i} how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:21.09,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　んなことどうでもいいって言ってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit dragging the past around\Nwith you and do the job you have now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,昔のことなんて何時までも引っ張ってないで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:25.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今やるべきことをやりなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yozora...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.20,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0}... If only {\i1}you{\i} weren't here, I'd already be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:37.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様さえ　貴様さえいなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:38.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今頃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:46.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,柏崎星奈のアホ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kashiwazaki Sena, you {\i1}jerk!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おい　夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Yozora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"If only {\i1}you{\i} weren't here," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:58.18,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様さえいなければ…か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:20:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate her, but you know, I've\Nnever once wished she were {\i1}gone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:01.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わたし　あいつのこと大嫌いだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:06.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いなければいいって思ったこと一度もないんだけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yozora?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:26.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I left my bag in the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:29.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,部室にかばんを置いたままだったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:30.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodaka, who do you want to be\NHirotaka's old friend? Kuya or Kotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:41.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹はどっちがいいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:45.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,広孝と仲がよかったのは 空也か小太郎か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter which one,\Nas long as the story's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,話が面白ければ　どっちでもいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:52.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私は　小鷹と幼なじみがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is more important to you, Kodaka?\NOur memories of ten years ago, or now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:59.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹は10年前の思い出と今　どっちが大事なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make a choice like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.39,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,選べねえよ　そんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はっきりしないな　お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:06.15,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　お前はどうなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is more important to you,\NYozora? Ten years ago, or now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:10.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空は　10年前と今　どっちが大事なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの　10年前に決まっている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean the present isn't important?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:16.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら今は大事じゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a toughie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,困ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:23.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:28.72,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"The Moon Rises in the Sky"\N\N"By: Mikazuki Yozora"\N\N"Draft 3"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:34.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! This is a piece of cake for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:38.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私にかかれば造作もないことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotaro fits right into the original\Nstory as a brother two years younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:41.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小太郎も二つ下の弟として
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:44.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,当初にストリーに自然に溶けこんでますね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika likes this one better, too!\NGood work, Yozora-{\i1}sempai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:46.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理科もこっちのほうが好きです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:48.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お疲れ様でした　夜空先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work, Anego.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:51.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お勤めご苦労様です　姉御
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I assume there\Nare no more complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:56.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　これで文句はないな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:22:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's get down to filming this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:22:00.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それでは　早速撮影に行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah!\N- Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:01.18,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張ろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:02.18,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,参りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't help but be a\Nmasterpiece, since I'm in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:05.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしが出てる時点で名作間違いなしだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:06.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ　肉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:09.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これ　どこで見たような気がするな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've seen this somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:33.01,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,光ったはずの星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:33.09,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikatta hazu no ano hoshi{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:36.23,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,迷った雲が邪魔して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:38.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mayotta kumo ga jama shite mienaku naru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:38.33,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見えなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:42.09,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nani wo shinjitara ii?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:41.62,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何を信じたらいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:45.94,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fuantei sugiru sekai de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:46.04,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不安定すぎる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:51.78,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sodatta takaramono kowashikaketeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.06,0:22:51.14,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,育った宝物壊しかけてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:54.70,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なくすのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:55.88,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nakusu no ga kowakute{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:22:57.53,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不条理だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:22:59.15,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fujouri datte tameiki tsuki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:22:58.84,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ため息つき
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:23:02.20,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうにかどうで足掻いてた日々
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:02.42,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Torikago de agaiteta hibi{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:08.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onaji sora wo miageteta n da bokura wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:06.61,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ空を見上げてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.89,0:23:08.54,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:11.86,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君の手を握った時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:14.94,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kimi no te wo nigitta{\i}\N{\i1}toki nigirikaeshite kureta ne{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:15.05,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,握り返してくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:21.48,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsunagatta kono te wa{\i}\N{\i1}donna hane yori tsuyoi n da{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:18.19,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,繋がったこの手は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:21.66,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな羽より強いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:28.02,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubasa nante nakutatte motto takaku toberu kara{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:24.81,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,翼だってなくったって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:28.10,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと高く飛べるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:31.42,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kitto ima nara daijoubu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:31.34,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと今なら大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:36.46,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大空輝く星を掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:37.15,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oozora kagayaku hoshi wo tsukamou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, mademoiselle Yozora, you look so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:43.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マドモアゼル夜空　とても切ないね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.77,0:23:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oui!{\i} I think it's important for Yozora\Nto be more open with her feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:48.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空はもっと素直になることが大切だと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.37,0:23:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, you must openly\Nshare your {\i1}amour,{\i} like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:53.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　僕達のように素直にアムール伝えるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.77,0:23:56.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とてもジュテームだよ　ステファ二ー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:23:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}je t'aime{\i} you so much, Stéphanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}je t'aime{\i} you too, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:59.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わたしもジュテームだわ　ジョナサン
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:24:09.49,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an8\pos(640,340)}"{\c&H8527E5&}Stray {\c&H1DD9A8&}Cats {\c&H0CEAF9&}Overheat{\c&HFFFFFF&}"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "Stray Cats Overheat."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:02.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,次回　「迷い猫　オーバーヒート」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:05.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の股間も　オーバーヒート
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My loins are overheating too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C'est si bon! C'est si bon!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.49,0:24:08.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,セシボーン　セシボーン
